Package bibliothek.extension.gui.dock.theme

Contains some DockThemes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BubbleTheme
    A theme using a lot of eye-candy.
    EclipseTheme
    A theme imitating the look and feel of the Eclipse-IDE.
    FlatTheme
    A theme that uses very few borders.
    IdentifiedColorScheme
    A ColorScheme that is wrapped around another scheme.
    SmoothTheme
    This theme uses the SmoothDefaultTitleFactory to create some titles which smoothly changes their color.

Package bibliothek.extension.gui.dock.theme Description

Contains some DockThemes. DockThemes can be exchanged using DockController.setTheme(bibliothek.gui.DockTheme).
